Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:24.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:29.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎しみに　変わって行く前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:31.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもそうだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:36.39,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:39.22,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.33,0:01:41.55,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:45.31,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.45,0:01:49.79,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:57.41,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壊しあって　解り合ったことも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:01:59.22,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:02.66,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.79,0:02:07.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:13.41,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:18.15,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:24.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:30.24,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って君はつぶやいて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:34.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じる事が怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:37.15,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:40.91,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:45.93,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当の愛を知るだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:24.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛說愛「過於沉重」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:29.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在轉變成恨之前　把它拒絕於心門之外…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:31.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬物皆是如此吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:36.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是把不合時宜的事隱藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:39.22,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是冒牌貨的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.33,0:01:41.55,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在扭曲了的窘迫時代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:45.31,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連本應定下約定的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.45,0:01:49.79,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會毫無察覺地擦肩而過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:57.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那開始崩壞但曾經互相理解的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:01:59.22,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其撇下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:02.66,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的末路嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.79,0:02:07.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中不服　想與之對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:13.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要從當初墮落的印象中逃離開去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:18.15,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　就算歷經千百次也要找出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:24.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的雙眸　你手中的余溫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:30.24,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小聲嘟囔著「愛總是讓我遍體鱗傷…」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:34.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因畏懼堅信不疑的事而哭過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:37.15,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道軟弱才能變強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:40.91,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕堅信不疑地走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:45.93,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是愛的真諦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:57.12,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}#09 無法逝去的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  是我的失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.02,0:00:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.20,0:00:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.04,0:00:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的扭曲點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我們要用Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將世界的扭曲破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.13,0:00:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne的發展型？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.13,0:00:22.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Arche Gundam：權天使高達，Throne系列的發展型）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.34,0:00:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難…難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:28.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  這就開戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.06,0:00:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam之間盛大的戰爭！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧  Fang
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.90,0:00:41.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.05,0:00:43.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與以前大不相同了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不來勁啊  Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還活著嗎  阿里·阿爾·沙謝斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  但拜你們所賜  半個肩膀燒焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.61,0:01:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的命還遠遠不夠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要拿你的性命來為再生治療付賬！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.12,0:02:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO和Seravee處於戰鬥狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.39,0:03:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然被A-LAWS盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派Gundam過去果然沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯繫待機中的阿里路亞他們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.04,0:03:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧  克魯吉斯的小鬼 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩的仇人就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來為他報一箭之仇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:44.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右眼看不見還跑到戰場上作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.55,0:03:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏手臂…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲開了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fang
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起升天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:29.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四對一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:38.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形勢十分不利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  特瑞亞  皇小姐發來了歸艦命令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼制止我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是洛克恩的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的…仇人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:05:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還活著…阿里·阿爾·沙謝斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克魯吉斯的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個倔強的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.36,0:05:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  必須這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李傑尼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜你所賜派對搞得一團糟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惹怒特瑞亞·埃德的可是你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.09,0:05:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好勸的話  本可能把他拉到我們陣營的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧得我事先做了這麼多準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望他們與我們對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being活動得越頻繁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS就越會遵照輿論的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行動也就變得順理成章
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.57,0:05:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.17,0:05:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區一個卡塔隆太不過癮了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為戰鬥用而出生的我就沒出場機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twin-Drive系統
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭載了兩個GN Drive的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是Celestial Being獨立開發的產品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是與TRANS-AM系統一樣  同屬伊奧利亞·修亨伯格的遺產
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:22.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪個都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那種性能  遠比不上Gadessa
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:27.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Gadessa：GNZ-003  改革者開發的機體  機師為李維夫·李拜巴爾）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次戰鬥中李維夫·李拜巴爾會證明的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要準備讓我出場啊  李本茲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那他們安然逃離了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與改革者的對立  會促使變革的加速
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很期待會如何發展呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準尉  感覺怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞您費心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於我的身體  你沒有聽說什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓我打聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…十分感謝體諒我的難處
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:27.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到部隊會展開追擊Gundam作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲·哈萊維
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4年前由於Gundam的攻擊失去了所有親人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自身也遭受到毒性GN粒子的輻射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,細胞受到損害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是復仇嗎？  如此年輕就踏上戰場的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個與華麗的禮服如此相配的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個少年是Celestial Being的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·清榮…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架機體…MR.武士道！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam各機收容完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始全部GN Drive對托勒密的對接
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回宇宙？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據我的推測  12小時以內敵人會展開包圍網式的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:38.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是逃不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  回到拉格朗日3
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能修補Gundam以及得到支援機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特  米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能開始脫離大氣層的程序嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到路易絲了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很偶然的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:05.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  還打聽了一些你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴她你在宇宙工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒和她聯繫過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架Gundam是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有哥哥的仇人又是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如我所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛那架Gundam的阿里·阿爾·沙謝斯奪走了洛克恩的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:30.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里·阿爾·沙謝斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請說得更詳細些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯密爾諾夫少尉  哈萊維準尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全返回
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:52.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據失去Gundam的地點  經過時間以及移動速度計算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推測出敵艦會航行於這片區域
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:10:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我隊會派出6架Trilobite包圍整個區域
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦發現敵艦立刻進行攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制空權確保了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派2個MS小隊足夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們該不會直接從海裡鑽出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望把戰術與以往的例子相關聯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦曾突破了大氣層  降落到地面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼反過來也行有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的想法也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的GN Drive有個名叫TRANS-AM的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.97,0:10:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高濃度粒子全面解放的系統
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用這一技術恐怕就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建議與部署在同步衛星軌道上的部隊配合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方的作戰指揮官也看穿了剛剛的正規戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:50.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是無禮  你想愚弄身為長官的我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我獲得了許可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是One-man Amry嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:10:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與Mr.武士道不同 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保證會遵照上校的指示行事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是令人欣慰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:09.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.97,0:11:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥為了幫家人復仇盯上了沙謝斯那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在笑什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私仇比改變世界都重要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真像哥哥的作風
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:22.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不滿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我很尊敬他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人都死了10多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不可能糾結這麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算仇人就在眼前嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾隸屬於KBSA  那個奪去你家人生命的組織
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.59,0:11:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用做到這個程度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是必須說的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的  我要代替神完成未盡的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:11:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  你居然怕死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是褻瀆神靈的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:10.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰爭是奉獻給神的一次聖戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對蔑視傳統  毀壞著神的土地的非信仰者們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為神的代言人  我們將揮下制裁的鐵錘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那時候  我勸阻了同伴的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩  不  尼爾·迪蘭地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就不會成為Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你能勸得了一時  恐怖襲擊終究還是會發生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事是躲不過的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:48.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:50.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是過去的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.94,0:12:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後悔過去也無濟於事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我們不是為了過去  而是為了未來而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵照自己堅信的正義而活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這真的與未來相連嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.49,0:13:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與改革者敵對…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有真正的未來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是在開發新型機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉…不  現在是叫Mr.武士道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人擅自這麼叫的  實在麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你挺喜歡這名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  今天有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來祝賀你就任開發主任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.90,0:13:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  希望你把那台還在試作階段的機體交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.01,0:13:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這才是你來的目的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對它有什麼要求嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最快的速度和最強的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:08.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:14.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為交換  你一定要將Celestial Being解決掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然  我只是為此而活著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  現在你所屬的部隊不是正在作戰中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對艦隊戰沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都將作戰內容看得如此透徹了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍛煉過洞察力了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.65,0:14:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS隊全體出擊  Trilobite各機已到達索敵區域
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  在發現敵艦的同時開始作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望您明白我跟本次作戰毫無關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你的便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.23,0:14:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會加油的  上校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是Gadessa
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是新型機嗎  A-LAWS到底接受了多少捐款
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  Celestial Being將如何應對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒向皇·李·諾瑞加報告嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在整理頭緒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我之前的下文吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找到的扭曲點是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變革總是伴有傷痛  你們不也是這麼過來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要管別的  自己去做不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是為計劃而生的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.52,0:15:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是被伊奧里亞那個老爺子託付了Gundam的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們已經成了伊奧里亞的計劃的障礙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.59,0:15:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認到6台敵人的水中用MA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請各位到指定位置就位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.31,0:16:07.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.47,0:16:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人包圍住托勒密並逐漸接近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預計他們開始攻擊的時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.31,0:16:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0024
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人預測到我們在赤道上了…真有一手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐到輔助席上去吧  晃動會很大的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密  採取急速上浮姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從中東灣直接飛進宇宙  以逃脫A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預計敵人開始攻擊的時間只剩下0004了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不行  要拖到最後一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人部隊有反應了  是大型魚雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios  Cherudim  Seravee開始啟動TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解  TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field最大程度展開  托勒密緊急上浮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮向爆炸點的上方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:11.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想擊中！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密轉為飛行模式！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦從海面急速上浮  還在上升！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他  他們是真的想突破大氣層嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我的預測還要早  是利用Trilobite的攻擊為初期加速了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計算出敵艦的上升路線
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  這種速度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是艦船的速度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了…瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:18:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒用啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有炮口全部打開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齊射！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:12.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別逃  Celestial Being！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是何等大膽的戰術  看來果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦前行路線出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李拜巴爾上尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需要將其上升角度改變3度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對Gadessa來說易如反掌！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高度突破六百千米了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:18:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就照這樣脫離大氣層
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.87,0:18:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角度被改變了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:19:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的指揮官實在有一手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.94,0:19:05.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰的第一序列結束  敵人的TRANS-AM有時間限制
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.26,0:19:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就看傑江中校的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密現在高度一萬千米  已越過低軌道環了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敵人部隊的攻擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.83,0:19:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道被埋伏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM即將突破時限
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:26.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再啟動之前GN Field將消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船體上部中彈！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人數量多少？
