Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:37.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在預測範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的粒子用完了  一口氣擊潰他們！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人MS接近！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Gundam！
