Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.73,0:20:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一鼓作氣瞄準主艦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO  驅逐目標！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊沉敵艦了！
