Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預測很準確啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算逃出來了
